  <Features
    id="features"
    title="Why should I enter the Oasis?"
    subtitle="We approach partnerships a bit differently than the traditional crowd. We aren't afraid to break molds and add soul into our work and partnerships. We believe that the best partnerships are built on trust and a shared vision. We are looking for partners who are willing to take risks and build something great together."
